O  Leo Davidson ,enas amerikanos astronayths,einai ypeythinos ekpaideyshs mias neas genias piloton.oi pilotoi aytoi einai pithikoi,poy mathainoyn na odhgoyn mikra diasthmoploia.kata th diarkeia mias tetoias anagnoristikhs pthshs pros enan agnosto planhth,to mikro diasthmoploio xaneithn epafh toy me ton pyrgo elegxoy.etsi o leo vgainei o idios sto diasthma gia na vrei to xameno oxhma.oi asxhmes synthikes omos tha ton anagasoyn na kanei anagastikh prosgeiosh s`enan parakseno planhth.ekei tha vrethei pagideymenos s`enan traxykai protogono xoris ixnos prohgoymenoy politismoy.den tha argish omos na anakalhpsei oti ston planhth ayto oi pithikoi exoyn ton elegxo,eno oi anthropoi einai kynhghmenoi kai sklavomenoi
